---
// Case Studies section for CRE industry page
---

<section id="case-studies" class="cre-case-studies-section">
  <div class="cre-case-studies-container">
    <span class="section-label">SUCCESS IN CRE</span>
    <h2 class="cre-case-studies-headline">
      Real outcomes from CRE firms we work with
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-case-studies-grid">
      <!-- Case Study 1 -->
      <a href="/case-studies/deal-intelligence-platform" class="cre-case-study-card">
        <span class="cre-case-meta">Regional Investment Firm</span>
        <h3 class="cre-case-title">
          Regional investment firm unifies deal flow and accelerates evaluation by 67%
        </h3>
        <p class="cre-case-description">
          Built a unified deal intelligence platform that connected broker networks, automated underwriting workflows, and provided real-time pipeline visibility. The firm now evaluates deals in 6 days instead of 18.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-case-outcome">
          <span class="cre-outcome-value">6-day reduction</span>
          <span class="cre-outcome-label">in underwriting cycle</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Case Study 2 -->
      <a href="/case-studies/construction-automation" class="cre-case-study-card">
        <span class="cre-case-meta">Multi-Asset CRE Firm</span>
        <h3 class="cre-case-title">
          Multi-asset CRE firm closes 40% more qualified deals with automated sourcing
        </h3>
        <p class="cre-case-description">
          Implemented intelligent deal sourcing system that aggregates opportunities from multiple channels, automatically qualifies leads, and matches deals to buyer profiles. Deal flow increased 3x while maintaining quality.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-case-outcome">
          <span class="cre-outcome-value">40% more</span>
          <span class="cre-outcome-label">qualified deals closed</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Case Study 3 -->
      <a href="/case-studies/financial-automation" class="cre-case-study-card">
        <span class="cre-case-meta">Portfolio Management Firm</span>
        <h3 class="cre-case-title">
          Portfolio management firm eliminates manual reporting overhead
        </h3>
        <p class="cre-case-description">
          Automated investor reporting system that generates portfolio performance reports on-demand. Reports that previously took 3-5 days to compile now generate in minutes, with zero manual data entry.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-case-outcome">
          <span class="cre-outcome-value">Zero manual</span>
          <span class="cre-outcome-label">reporting overhead</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-case-studies-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-case-studies-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-case-studies-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-case-studies-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-case-study-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    padding: 32px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover .cre-case-meta {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover .cre-case-title {
    color: #000000;
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover .cre-case-description {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover .cre-outcome-value {
    color: #0EA5E9;
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover .cre-outcome-label {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  .cre-case-meta {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-case-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-case-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    flex-grow: 1;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-case-outcome {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    transition: border-color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-case-study-card:hover .cre-case-outcome {
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .cre-outcome-value {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #0EA5E9;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-outcome-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    text-transform: lowercase;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-case-studies-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-case-studies-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-case-study-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

